"Wait... something is not right. Karrag is not fighting back. He is nothing "
"but an illusion!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_The_Court_of_Karrag.cfg:472
